WEBVTT

00:00:27.640 --> 00:00:30.216
and left many people longing
for earlier decades,

00:00:30.240 --> 00:00:33.560
when the world seemed safer,
cleaner and more equal.

00:00:34.560 --> 00:00:38.136
But is this a sensible way
to understand the human condition

00:00:38.160 --> 00:00:40.136
in the 21st century?

00:00:40.160 --> 00:00:42.936
As Franklin Pierce Adams pointed out,

00:00:42.960 --> 00:00:45.656
"Nothing is more responsible
for the good old days

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:46.896
than a bad memory."

00:00:46.920 --> 00:00:49.656
(Laughter)

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:53.056
You can always fool yourself
into seeing a decline

00:00:53.080 --> 00:00:55.776
if you compare bleeding
headlines of the present

00:00:55.800 --> 00:00:58.896
with rose-tinted images of the past.

00:00:58.920 --> 00:01:01.336
What does the trajectory
of the world look like